profile:
JonesCo Contracting Inc. is pleased to provide a full spectrum of innovative, cost effective and energy efficient solutions for new home construction and home renovations. We have been involved in new home building and residential construction since 2004, and work continuously to improve our knowledge and refine our processes to meet the ever-evolving needs of Atlantic Canadians.

We pride ourselves in offering high-quality craftsmanship, knowledgeable tradespeople and unique solutions to each project we undertake. We strive to be the best in our industry by offering a wide array of services from renovation to new construction, outdoor living areas to garages. At JonesCo we have the knowledge and expertise to tackle any project presented, and believe that contracting any project is a process and not an “event” that happens. Throughout the process we keep clients informed, up-to-date, and involved.

Simply put, we promise that our clients receive the best possible service, at greater value than our competition.
